{"tid":1070072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊獵頭 覺得HR 好撚閪 好撚濕鳩 好撚仆街","createTime":"2019-03-20T11:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T12:16:10.000Z","uid":198216,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70da39bebebc737b47002fd735b9c0734f3267cb","tid":1070072,"uid":198216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:24:00.000Z","msg":"兩個月前就湊緊個candidate<br />\n年資20年左右 好stable 好有經驗<br />\n本身佢人工5字頭<br />\n就幫佢嗌5字尾人工 （預佢一定會中5字尾人工）<br />\nHR 收到佢份profile<br />\n就即刻想約佢<br />\n但個傻鳩HR又搞佐成半個月先arrange 到 interview<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦 約完見完 line manager<br />\n人工就即刻比HR 壓到 5字中<br />\n皆因為HR 拎唔到budget<br />\n我真心覺得唔好意思 就同candidate講返<br />\nCandidate又肯accept<br />\n之後Final in 見 HR <br />\nHR 一句撻埋去話 4字尾 接唔接受<br />\n好啦 candidate 問清楚哂 個HR所有details嘢<br />\nCandidate 佢自己都ok 話可以接受 <br />\n（我無氹過或水個candidate)<br />\n好啦 HR 話positive 開始正式process offer<br />\n<br />\n本身預一個月前就會收到offer<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n追佐成個一個星期 日日打比HR <br />\n屌佢老母又唔撚聽電話又唔撚吊又話process 緊offer<br />\n又話 等上面批<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果 打黎話 Team Head 想再做多次 Interview <br />\n又問個價位可唔可以再傾吓<br />\n<br />\n屌！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都唔好意思再聯絡個candidate <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 究竟你有係心請人架仆街冥通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf5f25d08805449438e8dae9a53847fcce53cab","tid":1070072,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:28:24.000Z","msg":"咁你幫佢叫高D 你自己抽佣都多D啦, 講到自己好似好偉大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a7115293703d83b607cf34bcd32e8ea836b8f6","tid":1070072,"uid":198216,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid